---
title: Smart Mexican-Inspired Turkey Salad with Lime Crema Dressing
description: No longer just the dollop on top of your taco, lime crema is the star of this spicy turkey salad! The smooth, creamy, zippy dressing tangos with smoky chipotle heat for a perfectly balanced bite every time!

